CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: J-Star Holding Co. is a technology-driven business, offering cutting edge technology and manufacturing expertise in carbon composite to their customers. Our Predecessor Group was established in 1970 and we have accumulated over 50 years know-how in the material composite industry. Many of our products are directly or indirectly supplied to renowned international sports brand owners. We primarily generate revenue through three divisions and revenue streams, namely (i) sales of bicycles parts of sports bicycle and electric bicycle, (ii) sales of rackets for use in tennis, badminton, squash and beach tennis, and (iii) sales of other products, which mainly include structural parts of automobile, other sporting goods and healthcare products.
